      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "<code>... if all the exceptions belong to the same class hierarchy, you can simply catch that base exception type.</code> Not really. Doing so, you will catch all other - and maybe unwanted - children of the base type. Sementically, this is different."
    }, {
      "owner" : {
