      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "BTW catch clauses are handled in order so if you put a parent exception class before a child class then it&#39;s never called eg:  try {    ... } catch (Exception e) {    someCode(); } catch (RepositoryException re) {    // never reached }"
