    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Within Java 7 you can define multiple catch clauses like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>catch (IllegalArgumentException | SecurityException e)\n{\n    ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
