    "question_id" : 3495926,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>It is very simple:</p>\n<pre><code>try { \n  // Your code here.\n} catch (IllegalArgumentException | SecurityException | IllegalAccessException |\n            NoSuchFieldException e) { \n  // Handle exception here.\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
